{"tid":2081310,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"明白左唔霸住人，祝人幸福。依種感覺係好舒適。","createTime":"2020-06-27T06:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T13:57:28.000Z","uid":201062,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ab451a86e1d43f981e3c905c8fb6094d636a00","tid":2081310,"uid":201062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"好多謝在我苦戀緊果時妳陪伴我半年，慢慢好似鐘意咗你。我其實唔肯定係咪戀愛果種鐘意，但在我心中你係頭三名最重要的女人。<br />\n<br />\n    好想時間停留在我地一班人入Camp玩果兩日，仲拖到你手玩遊戲，之後我地又單獨出街食飯，幾乎日日都講心事。我明白我地只係最高層次的友誼，係差少少。<br />\n    <br />\n    上星期六，你同我講話出咗pool，話朋友介紹認識的，只認識左兩星期。我知你好迷佢，我只有一個願望，就係你幸福。<br />\n<br />\n     講真，認識就係緣份。深交就係好有緣。再到拍拖、結婚。其實行曬完整cycle又有幾多個。所以，我選擇做唔出聲做你的朋友，可能仲好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4978a252eb295986f0b1da3cf4005680263ed9","tid":2081310,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"1dfef73494f13f42807174862ce7fb3db437eca9","tid":2081310,"uid":159103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T06:22:54.000Z","msg":"共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3f21247dbce488912c5e0e58a0529395edb73d","tid":2081310,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:31:32.000Z","msg":"明白放過你是放過自己 這個道理"},{"pid":"274e80becc9319012f843b5337df64ffc2dc4e78","tid":2081310,"uid":57255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"最高層次既友誼，可能只係差拍拖少少，但你有無諗過，中間係隔住一塊玻璃，永遠都穿唔過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd9ac818b39d3aeef25f4b4f9714f5e6c667dc6","tid":2081310,"uid":201062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274e80becc9319012f843b5337df64ffc2dc4e78","tid":2081310,"uid":57255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"最高層次既友誼，可能只係差拍拖少少，但你有無諗過，中間係隔住一塊玻璃，永遠都穿唔過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"所以咪算，佢現在好快樂，我都仲係佢好朋友，其實最好了。"},{"pid":"cd47ca68018d4427463348710d5d67e1d6e9fb2c","tid":2081310,"uid":72991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:55:22.000Z","msg":"咪包裝得咁靚啦<br />\n唔係唔霸住，係霸唔住<br />\n我都係，面對同承認啦"},{"pid":"6363e44f58a323627bb0690675af3cc2fe444df0","tid":2081310,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}